comments.author: ekline
comments.body:
The [IANA EtherTypes](https://www.iana.org/assignments/ieee-802-numbers/ieee-802-numbers.xhtml) page shows no evidence of an allocation for anything Bundle/BP/Licklider/LTP related.

Bouncing through [various IEEE](https://regauth.standards.ieee.org/standards-ra-web/pub/view.html#registries) pages lands on [this text file](https://[standards-oui.ieee.org/ethertype/eth.txt](https://standards-oui.ieee.org/ethertype/eth.txt), which seems to be an exhaustive list.  No evidence of an allocation for anything Bundle/BP/Licklider/LTP related here either.
